WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.303
To ground this, engage in a rigorous analytical challenge. Identify

00:00:04.303 --> 00:00:08.605
a recent leadership failure within your organization. Map the root

00:00:08.605 --> 00:00:12.908
cause of that failure to a specific value incongruence. What

00:00:12.908 --> 00:00:17.210
objective variables were present? What was the root cause hypothesis?

00:00:17.210 --> 00:00:21.513
What solution variables were analyzed? Deploying structured cognitive protocols under

00:00:21.513 --> 00:00:25.815
pressure ensures analytical precision over reactive assumptions.
